            </td>
            <td style="text-align:right; vertical-align:middle; color:#ffffff; font-size:0.9rem;">
              Application Received
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td style="padding:20px;">
        <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size:1.1rem; color:#0f1724;">Dear {{Full_name}},</h1>

        <p style="margin:0 0 14px; color:#5b6b77; font-size:1rem;">
          Thank you for applying to <strong style="color:#026866;">Atharv Yogshala</strong>. We’ve received your application for the
          <strong style="color:#026866;">{{Course_Name}}</strong>.
        </p>

        <table role="presentation" width="100%" style="margin-top:12px; border:1px solid #eef3f6; border-radius:8px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:14px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 10px; color:#253241; font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;">Application details</p>

              <table role="presentation" width="100%" style="font-size:14px; color:#5b6b77;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0; width:45%;">Course:</td>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0;"><strong>10 Days Yoga & Meditation Retreat in Rishikesh</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0; width:45%;">Course Date:</td>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0;"><strong>{{Course_Date}} {{Year}}</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0;">Accommodation Type:</td>
                  <td style="padding:6px 0;"><strong>{{Acc.Type}}</strong></td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:12px 0 0; color:#6b7780; font-size:14px;">
                One of our application managers will review your application and get in touch with you shortly. <br>
                If you have any questions in the meantime, reach us on
                <a href="https://wa.me/918077047879" style="color:#0f72ff; text-decoration:none;">+91-8077047879</a> (Phone & WhatsApp)
                or reply to this email.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <p style="margin:16px 0 0; color:#5b6b77; font-size:0.9rem;">
          We look forward to getting to know you and welcoming you to <strong>Atharv Yogshala</strong>.
        </p>

        <p style="margin:18px 0 0; color:#5b6b77; font-size:0.9rem;">
          Kind regards,<br>
          <strong>The Atharv Yogshala Team</strong><br>
          <a href="https://atharvyogshala.com/" style="color:#0f72ff; text-decoration:none;">www.atharvyogshala.com</a>
        </p>
        <p style="margin:18px 0 0; color:#5b6b77; font-size:0.9rem;">
          <strong>Need urgent help?</strong><br>+91-8077047879 (Phone & WhatsApp)
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
       <td style="padding:0px 24px 24px; background:#fbfdff;">
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/atharv_yoga_school/" style="margin-right:10px; color:#0f72ff; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.8rem;">Instagram</a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/atharvyogashala" style="margin-right:10px; color:#0f72ff; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.8rem;">Facebook</a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@atharvyogshala" style="color:#0f72ff; text-decoration:none; font-size:0.8rem;">YouTube</a>
            </td>
    </tr>
    
    <tr>
      <td style="padding:12px 24px 28px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#9aa6af;">
        &copy; 2018-2025 — Atharv Yogshala, India
